A minimalistic vertical dock bar floating against a clean, muted gradient background in soft grays and teals, featuring a glowing circular timer icon with a subtle radial progress ring showing roughly one-sixth completion, surrounded by abstract geometric app icons in flat colors arranged in a neat vertical stack, the timer emanates a gentle pulsing glow suggesting urgency and focus, small particles of light drift upward from the timer like sand in an hourglass reversed, the composition emphasizes negative space and precision, with thin drop shadows adding subtle depth, the overall mood is calm productivity and digital zen.
